1
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,520
Where is he?

2
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,560
Where is Jiadong?

3
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:20,730
What's the rush?

4
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,000
You promised me.

5
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,440
Here he is.

6
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,640
Jiadong!

7
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,380
Don't move.

8
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,240
Jiadong!

9
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:39,900
Don't move!

10
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:42,440
Luo Wang!

11
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,520
You tortured him!

12
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,009
What did you expect?

13
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,500
Did you think I invited him

14
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,360
to the station

15
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,680
for a feast?

16
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,289
Lin Wangshu.

17
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,360
I did what I promised.

18
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,039
What about your promise?

19
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,900
So this is Luo Wang's backup plan.

20
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,160
Go!

21
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,800
Tell him to let him go first.

22
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,160
As long as I see him leave safely,

23
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,760
I will go with you right away.

24
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,840
And then I will marry you.

25
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,520
Wangshu.

26
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,560
No.

27
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,930
You can't marry him.

28
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,960
Brother Jiadong, I'm sorry.

29
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,760
I have no choice.

30
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,200
For my sake, Luo Wang

31
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,240
was willing to risk

32
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,240
being killed by Yamada to let you go.

33
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,000
I must keep my promise.

34
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,160
Luo Wang is too wicked.

35
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,960
Anyone who dares to betray the Great Japanese Empire

36
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,840
must not live.

37
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,579
If Luo Wang dares to let him go,

38
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,100
kill him immediately.

39
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,640
Understood.

40
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:05,800
Let him go now.

41
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,200
I said as long as he gets out safely,

42
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,320
I'll go with you.

43
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,740
Don't lie to me.

44
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,120
Okay.

45
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,760
Brother Jiadong.

46
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,000
My brother is waiting for you in Lane One on the right.

47
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,560
Go quickly.

48
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,890
Be careful. Be careful.

49
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,440
Are you done?

50
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,440
Still hugging.

51
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,280
Go.

52
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,360
Get lost.

53
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,079
No matter what happened,

54
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:49,440
the two of us

55
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,840
can finally be together.

56
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,920
Right?

57
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,680
Luo Wang.

58
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:58,760
Chief.

59
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,280
Hurry.

60
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,400
Hurry.

61
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:08,730
Wangshu.

62
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,640
Take Jiadong away.

63
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,480
I'll wrap this up.

64
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,960
Brother, you must be careful.

65
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,760
Don't linger.

66
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,160
Retreat once you see Luo Wang is dead.

67
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:14,890
Don't worry.

68
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,920
Go. Hurry.

69
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,399
Luo Wang,

70
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:24,080
how dare you double-cross me?

71
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,280
Yamada.

72
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,680
You are just like me.

73
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,130
We've both been fooled.

74
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,700
Do you think you're smart?

75
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,920
You are a fool too.

76
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,840
How dare you betray me!

77
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,280
Today is the day you die.

78
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,400
Yamada!

79
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,800
That's right.

80
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,280
This is my ending for betraying my people,

81
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,720
being your dog,

82
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,880
and a traitor!

83
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,840
But don't forget,

84
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,360
This will be your end too!

85
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,160
Yamada!

86
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,320
Now,

87
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:30,040
how am I going to explain this to the headquarters?

88
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,940
It's all because of you, you fool!

89
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,080
Fool!

90
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,880
Lock down the docks and the city gates immediately.

91
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,140
Search the whole city.

92
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,760
Make sure to capture Chen Jiadong

93
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,880
and his accomplices.

94
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,740
Catch them all!

95
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,200
D-Director,

96
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,280
I don't think that's a good idea.

97
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,000
In the middle of the night,

98
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,600
a sudden citywide search...

99
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,720
What about the Malayan government?

100
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,460
What are you afraid of?

101
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,320
We have the Greater Japanese Empire

102
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,120
backing us up.

103
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,440
If we can't catch them...

104
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,680
You all must die.

105
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,080
Understood.

106
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,120
What are you waiting for?

107
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:12,780
Search.

108
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,400
Search every house.

109
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,159
How did it go, brother?

110
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,080
Luo Wang is dead.

111
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,360
Yamada shot him himself.

112
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,040
Great.

113
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,240
That traitor

114
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,120
finally died

115
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,200
at the hands of his Japanese master.

116
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,330
It is so satisfying.

117
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:51,980
It's a pity.

118
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,600
Yamada was heavily guarded,

119
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,130
so we couldn't kill him too.

120
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,700
It can't be helped.

121
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,159
Killing Luo Wang

122
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,290
is already a great success.

123
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,140
No need to take further risks.

124
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:02,880
True.

125
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,780
But I really didn't expect...

126
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,720
Such a dangerous plan

127
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,920
actually succeeded.

128
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,210
Jiadong, you're a real genius.

129
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,280
It also relied on everyone's cooperation

130
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,040
to succeed.

131
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,420
If it wasn't a last resort,

132
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,680
I wouldn't have wanted Wangshu

133
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,040
to deal with that bastard Luo Wang.

134
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,780
You were the one who risked your life.

135
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,280
Look at you.

136
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,920
You're covered in wounds.

137
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,680
That damn Luo Wang

138
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,880
deserves to die ten thousand times.

139
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,040
Wangshu.

140
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,360
Don't worry.

141
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,920
It's good enough that Luo Wang is dead.

142
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,850
These minor injuries are nothing.

143
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,600
Now Yamada definitely won't...

144
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,730
They won't let it go.

145
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,360
We need to think of a countermeasure quickly.

146
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:49,920
Right.

147
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,000
Now that Luo Wang has just died

148
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,920
and they're still in chaos,

149
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:55,780
we should get you out of the city as soon as possible.

150
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,760
Mr. Qin.

151
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,560
The Japanese have blocked the city gates

152
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,640
and are searching door to door

153
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:01,170
for Jiadong and the others.

154
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,200
What?

155
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,200
The Japanese are acting so presumptuously.

156
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:06,280
Does the Malayan government not care?

157
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,160
It seems our previous

158
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,160
guess was right.

159
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,600
The Japanese's influence

160
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,520
has already made the Malayan government

161
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,720
afraid to intervene.

162
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,140
That's why Yamada can be so domineering.

163
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,520
We can't delay any longer.

164
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,040
We should get you out

165
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,560
of Malaya as soon as possible.

166
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,600
The city gates and the docks

167
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,680
are all blocked by the Japanese.

168
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,840
How will they leave?

169
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,400
We can only race against the Japanese.

170
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,800
Yamada will definitely think

171
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,360
we'll do what we did last time

172
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,320
and take the land route.

173
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,520
Then tomorrow morning,

174
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,240
we'll leave on the earliest boat.

175
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:31,920
Okay.

176
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,000
Mr. Qin.

177
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,240
Even if we leave,

178
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,360
what about

179
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,480
you guys?

180
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,090
Don't worry about that.

181
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,960
Our Chinese Chamber of Commerce

182
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,559
has been in Malaya for so many years after all.

183
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,520
We might not have the ability right now

184
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,840
to confront the Japanese head-on,

185
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,960
but we still have the ability

186
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,220
to protect ourselves.

187
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,040
As long as the Japanese can't find you,

188
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:49,760
there's nothing

189
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,760
they can do to us.

190
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,120
Okay.

191
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:54,640
Mr. Qin,

192
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,800
Manager Zhao.

193
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,040
Thank you for your great kindness.

194
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,840
Until we meet again.

195
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,520
No need for formalities at a time like this.

196
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,080
If you can't leave, come right back.

197
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,740
We'll figure out another way.

198
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,000
Okay.

199
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,730
Until we meet again.

200
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,520
Mr. Lin,

201
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,480
I really didn't expect

202
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,120
to say goodbye to you at a time like this.

203
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,450
I hope we will see each other again one day.

204
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,920
We will meet again.

205
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:20,880
Slow down.

206
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,080
Search carefully.

207
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,000
Dad, sit.

208
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,320
With Yamada having so many men,

209
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,650
we can't board the ship.

210
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,610
Brother,

211
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,920
what do we do now?

212
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,580
Just wait a moment.

213
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,520
Wait for what?

214
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,080
I asked comrades from the organization to help

215
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,720
create some trouble for them.

216
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,920
If they could shoot him,

217
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,280
that would be even better.

218
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,440
Dad, Jiadong,

219
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,240
let's take a short break.

220
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:53,000
There will be movement soon.

221
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,040
Who is it?

222
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:58,920
Run!

223
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,240
Run! Someone is killing people!

224
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,960
Bastard!

225
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:01,880
Sorry.

226
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,120
Damn it.

227
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,500
Could it be that

228
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,450
Chen Jiadong and his men

229
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:15,880
don't want to escape,

230
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:18,560
but want to assassinate me instead?

231
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,360
Captain Rajan.

232
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,360
President.

233
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,400
The search team,

234
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,560
while searching house to house,

235
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,760
also encountered several rioters

236
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,760
shooting at them,

237
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,660
just like here.

238
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,840
They all ran away.

239
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,360
Outrageous!

240
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,000
Withdraw some men from the pier

241
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,320
to strengthen the search.

242
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:39,920
Yes.

243
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,320
President.

244
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,640
You should go too.

245
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,320
Yes.
